## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on self-reported data, which can be subject to bias and inaccuracies. Additionally, the lack of a standardized definition of "self-defense" complicates comparisons across studies. The estimates also vary widely due to differences in survey methodologies, sample sizes, and the populations surveyed. As such, any conclusions drawn from these data should be considered with caution.

